technical work, but helping others on that journey, especially with documentation,

00:31:00.520 --> 00:31:06.760
internal resources. But what I've seen is sometimes leadership up in the chain,

00:31:06.760 --> 00:31:11.640
so to speak, don't really see the value of that side of the work, as opposed to just

00:31:11.640 --> 00:31:16.199
getting that technical deadline done or getting that, you know, that piece. I don't know, I'm

