I just did it. I didn't go asking for permission. I didn't say, Hey, look, we should do this.

00:31:55.560 --> 00:32:01.000
I just did it. And when I did it, now I can show the results. I can be like, Hey, look,

00:32:01.959 --> 00:32:08.439
when my team members are out, the business can still continue because we have tools in place

00:32:08.439 --> 00:32:15.880
to help to support the team. When you give me someone new, my team, that person can learn

