science world. I would highly recommend the book Subtract because it's not always about what you

00:33:48.599 --> 00:33:56.119
need to do. It's also about what you need to stop, right? There was a time my team was building

00:33:56.119 --> 00:34:03.719
reports week after week, sending them out. We're spending all this time, and we didn't know what

00:34:03.719 --> 00:34:08.600
