00:34:08.600 --> 00:34:13.479
was a recommendation. This is something I learned from our CEO. She recommended this book to me.

00:34:14.840 --> 00:34:21.879
This is what she told me. She's like, look, don't send those reports. Just stop and see how many

00:34:21.879 --> 00:34:28.280
people come knocking at your door for that report. And that's exactly what I did to the point where

00:34:28.280 --> 00:34:34.840
now I have a policy in my team where if we think something is not being used the way it should be,

00:34:35.399 --> 00:34:41.719
we put it on what we call a 90-day pause list. We don't tell anybody. We put it on a 90-day

00:34:41.719 --> 00:34:47.479
